 # NLP Central Banks

## Project Overview
This project assesses the different layers of communication of central banks.

## Repository Structure

### 1. `lyna_work/` — BERTopic Analysis (Classical Speeches)
- `preprocessing.ipynb` — Data cleaning and preparation
- `topic_modelling.ipynb` — BERTopic modeling + figures
 This analysis was also conducted for the NLP class, which enabled me to learn about these techniques
(hence you will find there a document detailing the methodology used and answering other questions, do not take it into account) : 

 
### 1bis. `social_mediavsclassic.ipynb` (main branch)
- Descriptive statistics comparing central bank vs social media communication

### 2. `lisa_work/` — Word2Vec Embeddings
- `preprocessing.ipynb`
- `word2vec.ipynb` — Main analysis

### 3. `sofiene_work/` : for the last section of the analysis



